Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 犬美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳光是逃我怎麼明白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把理由說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:00:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那霸？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\bord2\be10\alpha255\fs70\pos(842,543)}孤單一人的{\fs120\c&HA194D8&}感{\c&H8B487F&}受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美 為什麼要把飯盆打翻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那叛逆的眼神是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢飛飯盆的是犬美妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是我親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也充分考慮到了營養均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有犬美妳那麼任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說妳是代表大家說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏 你也是這麼認為的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏你到底是站在哪一邊的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因為早餐的事在吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能像那樣互相溝通耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是「奔跑吧 動物世界」的收錄日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個節目是以響和犬美為中心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個樣子沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.18,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在聽嗎 犬美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美在節目裡人氣超高的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊 話說雪步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明狗就在附近 但妳好像沒什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已經不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 完全不怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來似乎沒什麼精神啊 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去做發聲練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼 這種說法未免太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說到這種地步 妳真不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實不是人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 氣死我了 我不管妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來錄製節目也隨便妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 阿響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎一如既往的大受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你負責的那個動物類節目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 託您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事不會有紕漏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一切都已辦的妥妥當當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍外景時領導也都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之後應該就可以讓我那霸響退出這節目了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您言重了 我剛進這行的時候就一直受到黑井社長的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請務必隨意吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝時我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑井社長親自出馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天Jupiter也要承蒙你照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我突然很想看看765PRO那幫人不像樣的哭喪臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 犬美要請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 那個…牠有點不太舒服的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人擔心呢對吧 阿響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有犬美在都沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有我一個人也會讓節目變得有趣起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真堅強啊 正因為很擔心所以才會逞強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這下頭痛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為代替 得去找一隻可以擔任主角的動物才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 就用牠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 是負責人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是布萊克·法爾希恩三世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道會出這種事 就事先準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然幫大忙了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過跟犬美比起來 好像有點太兇殘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠只是在緊張而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教啊 犬三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我那霸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布萊克·法爾希恩三世啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔乖喔 請多指教啊 犬三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊 犬三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4  3  2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是我那霸響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奔跑吧 動物世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:07:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是慣例的「動物探險隊」環節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會有一名新隊員加入喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這是犬三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來聽聽牠今天的幹勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 犬三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 今天會遇見怎樣的動物呢 真是期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我們打起精神 開始探險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美在的話我就不用這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對 我才不管什麼犬美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不在也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿響 之後會像以前一樣 換個地方繼續拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說今天會去池塘附近尋找動物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 剛才我聽導演說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天突然決定請Jupiter來當來賓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請他們？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是前來參加節目內其他環節的攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不會直接和妳有所接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道961RRO會耍什麼詭計 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會輸給那些只知道耍詐的小人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情況 千萬要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我那霸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外景巴士坐不下了 導演叫我用別的車載妳過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的製作人還沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後他會坐巴士過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬君 冬馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗 看這邊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太你最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你們跟Jupiter不會是第一次見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是現在絕讚走紅中的765PRO的大腕製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是765PRO？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了捧紅偶像做了不少卑鄙的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你被灌輸了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但765PRO不是這種事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們是絕對不會輸給961PRO的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖 那傢伙搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來關係變得很不錯嘛 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 那就是765PRO的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是張和事務所很相襯的臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那傢伙一個人在這 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 計劃已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂革命 永遠都是激進的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為需要一口氣改變一切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人說了是在池塘附近攝影來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是受人指使而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人指使？被誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 很沒精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小犬美一動不動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能叫一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無計可施呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿響明明一直都在說是為了犬美牠們才努力工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這裡是765PRO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你是說阿響嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們這邊沒收到聯絡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…在搭車移動的時候她擅自上了別的車然後就分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自上車？這怎麼可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打過阿響的手機了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影前她交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我還會再聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底為什麼就只有阿響不是坐外景巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是坐別的車子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我那霸小姐是擔當主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了要特殊待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 阿響不會要求這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是個就算自己的攝影結束了也會一直等到最後的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 現在的小孩確實讓人搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然製片方的人也在這裡所以說這話有點不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要走紅了 大家的態度都會有所轉變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣 我們事務所的偶像們可是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 大家都是這麼說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 導演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這情況就嘗試啟用別的偶像們來主持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Jupiter來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他們也很有人氣 作為代替來說非常合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次作為來賓前來也一定是什麼緣分 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然阿響毫無疑問是最合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是來的太晚的話 我們直播也有壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 我會想辦法找到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請再稍微等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都說到這地步了 那就等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們想在白天結束拍攝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 沒人過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想爬上去 但土質這麼鬆軟也根本不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這就跟製作人說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道961RRO會耍什麼詭計 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣下去趕不上攝影的話 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？把哈姆藏扔到崖壁的上面去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？跟犬美牠們聯絡 讓牠們前來營救？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的外景巴士犬美也能聞出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟犬美可是在吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.83,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY TRIAL DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.44,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY TRIAL DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿響 阿響
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.89,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WOW WOW WOW WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.67,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EVERY BOY DO IT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.25,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EVERY GIRL DO IT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.67,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH YEAH YEAH YEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:57.08,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今が始まる IT'S BRAND NEW STAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:57.08,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始 IT'S BRAND NEW STAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好只是陣雨的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了的話就以Jupiter為主開始攝影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.49,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢を刻んでくPURE HEARTBEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.49,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銘刻夢想 PURE HEARTBEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.39,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.22,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DRESS UP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷你環節和攝影不都很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.04,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LIGHT UP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.78,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対NEVER GIVE UP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.78,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對NEVER GIVE UP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是走紅的組合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 我也知道他們能圓滑周到的進入角色啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.64,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さあSTEP BY STEP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.64,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 STEP BY STEP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:13.24,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:13.24,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率性而為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.97,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さあGOOD BYE DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.97,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 GOOD BYE DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就因為今天跟犬美吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.37,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,REALにMETAMORPHOSE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.37,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的褪變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果什麼事都不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.54,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつだってI CAN GO NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.54,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時 I CAN GO NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美 為什麼就因為一餐飯而那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:30.71,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとCRAZY BURNING HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:30.71,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多的CRAZY BURNING HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.50,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY TRIAL DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.14,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY TRIAL DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:37.41,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力強くLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:37.41,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用盡全力的LIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.44,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EVERY BOY DO IT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.04,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EVERY GIRL DO IT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.35,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DON'T STOP MUSIC
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是獨自跑來這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠好像在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 我們聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美？我說…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是在說帶我們去阿響身邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 直到不久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的飯還是我一個個親手做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把討厭的食物切得很碎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在喜歡吃的食物裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近因為變得很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 犬美 貓吉 還有大家 來吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來要去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要好好看家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美說的不只是食物的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是營養均衡之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是想要在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻責備犬美 跟牠吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說了很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬美？為什麼妳會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來了 還沾了一身的泥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家對不起啊 我什麼都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 還是沒找到阿響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 幸虧一直在下雨也沒誤什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物探險隊的開場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Jupiter為主角重拍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到工作中來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽也真是不識趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明再下一會也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好 妳的睫毛可真長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑井先生 攝影即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟計劃中的一樣  Jupiter成為了擔當主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個765PRO的製作人 看起來相當不甘心呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是騙了那個小姑娘把她帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也完全不知道已經被帶走有一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這麼一回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7…765PRO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始我就覺得你的態度很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然會把實情全盤托出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是黑井社長對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴導演 讓他現在馬上中止攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓961PRO稱心如意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管理由如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們C級Production的偶像在拍攝途中消失是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter接過了這個爛攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有阻止的權利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想中止Jupiter的拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你只要把你那邊的偶像帶過來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做得到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:19:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿響！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心死了 阿響
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 製作人 導演 抱歉給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 反正也回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意 趕快重新做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很抱歉 但Jupiter今天已經可以收工了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 明明都排練的完美無缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 今天很開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 擅自玩消失又突然跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 黑井社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是實在是…肯定有什麼差錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你的交情也就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請等等 黑井社長！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是被765PRO的卑鄙手段給陰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是想讓你們白跑一趟來報上次的仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒打一耙也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘖 果然765PRO那群人真是無可救藥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶像就給我以實力決勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來開始正式拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 今天的「奔跑吧 動物世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然居然 有這麼多同伴一起參加喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實現在在這裡的大家都是我不可替代的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了 音無小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道謝的話不要謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去謝犬美牠們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牠們在山裡四處奔跑才找到阿響的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 阿響跟犬美牠們之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週會遇見怎樣的動物呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 探險開始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 大家跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟大家一起 今後也沒有什麼解決不了的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:49.11,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CATCH UP 見つけましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:49.11,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CATCH UP 出發尋找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:52.30,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳の中に映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:52.30,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映射在眼瞳之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.88,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミに その先の
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.88,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起 想要感受未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:58.04,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキを感じたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:58.04,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:00.48,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ストレートな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:00.48,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接無比的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:04.14,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止められない乙女の熱いハート
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:04.14,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法阻止的少女那熱情的heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:06.31,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出逢ったかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:06.31,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許已經遇到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:10.02,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の私から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:10.02,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.21,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おお 何くれさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.21,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:16.20,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進め 負けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:16.20,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進吧 不會認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:19.18,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここから始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:19.18,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.70,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手と手を繋いで 走り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.70,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握雙手 開始奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:26.57,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分たちの未来は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:26.57,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:30.89,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負けたり 凹んだ 自信ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:30.89,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會失敗 也許會失落 也沒沒有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:34.59,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界には夜のあとは昼だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:34.59,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個世界黑夜之後就是白天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.44,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び込ちゃえば 多分ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.44,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要勇敢面對 大概就ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的偶像大師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…錄影要用高畫質
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為備份要兩台同時拍攝…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪步妳這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:06.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四條小姐！下週我要在家裡看電視…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 下週請一定要收看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\be10\alpha255\fs120\pos(706,439)}真{\fs70}、真正{\c&H35065A&}的{\r\bord2\be10\alpha255\fs120\pos(627,436)}王子大人
